ound style layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsource","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNSource","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNImageSource":{"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNImageSource"},{"type":"text","text":" is a content source that is used for a georeferenced raster"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image to be shown on the map. The georeferenced image scales and rotates as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"user zooms and rotates the map. Images may also be used as icons or patterns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in a style layer. To register an image for use as an icon or pattern,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle\/setImage:forName:"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To configure a point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s image, use the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"type":"text","text":" class."}],"title":"MLNImageSource","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNImageSource","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnimagesource","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNImageSource"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource/initWithIdentifier:shape:options:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a shape source with an identifier, a shape, and dictionary of options"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the source."}],"type":"