Source"}],"title":"MLNRasterDEMSource","abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterDEMSource"},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies rasterized","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"digital elevation model","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(DEM) tiles to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tiles are defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conforms to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TileJSON specification","type":"text"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A raster DEM source is added to an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object along with one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNHillshadeStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNColorReliefStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. Use a hillshade","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"style layer to control the appearance of content supplied by the raster DEM source,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or a color relief style layer to render elevation data with a color ramp.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNRasterDEMSource","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnrasterdemsource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource":{"title":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Data source for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". This protocol defines two optional methods for fetching"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"data, one based on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"requestQueue"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","kind":"identifier"}]}}}